Bootstrapping:

1) Make a bootstrapped dataset
2) Calculate the statistic (mean, median, sd, etc.)
3) Keep track of that calculation
4) Repeat steps 1-3 MANY times 

Used to calculate standard error and confidence interval for the original mean


